body.name: UIKit
body.description:
UIView The basic view abstraction within UIKit. (Very Important)
UIButton 		Very useful for tapping.
UITextField 		This is how you get words from your users.
UIApplication 		Don't override this. You shouldn't ever need to.
UIScrollView 		Quite possibly the most important class in UIKit.
UITableView 		Nothing more than an awesome incarnation of UIScrollView.
UILabel 		For labeling things. Good name, right?
UIApplicationDelegate 		The protocol you should implement to make your UIApplication useful.
